spirit:component.spirit:name: PmodGPIO_axi_gpio_0_0

spirit:field.spirit:name: Channel-1 GPIO DATA
spirit:field.spirit:description: AXI GPIO Data Register. For each I/O bit programmed as input R - Reads value on the input pin. W - No effect. For each I/O bit programmed as output R - Reads value on GPIO_O pins W - Writes value to the corresponding AXI GPIO data register bit and output pin

spirit:field.spirit:name: Channel-1 GPIO TRI
spirit:field.spirit:description: AXI GPIO 3-State Control Register Each I/O pin of the AXI GPIO is individually programmable as an input or output For each of the bits 0 - I/O pin configured as output 1 - I/O pin configured as input

spirit:field.spirit:name: Channel-2 GPIO DATA
spirit:field.spirit:description: AXI GPIO Data Register. For each I/O bit programmed as input R - Reads value on the input pin. W - No effect. For each I/O bit programmed as output R - Reads value on GPIO_O pins W - Writes value to the corresponding AXI GPIO data register bit and output pin

spirit:field.spirit:name: Channel-2 GPIO TRI
spirit:field.spirit:description: AXI GPIO 3-State Control Register Each I/O pin of the AXI GPIO is individually programmable as an input or output For each of the bits 0 - I/O pin configured as output 1 - I/O pin configured as input

spirit:field.spirit:name: Global Interrupt Enable
spirit:field.spirit:description: Master enable for the device interrupt output 0 - Disabled 1 - Enabled

spirit:field.spirit:name: Channel-1 Interrupt Status
spirit:field.spirit:description: Channel 1 Interrupt Status 0 - No Channel 1 input interrupt 1 - Channel 1 input interrupt

spirit:field.spirit:name: Channel-2 Interrupt Status
spirit:field.spirit:description: Channel 2 Interrupt Status 0 - No Channel 2 input interrupt 1 - Channel 2 input interrupt

spirit:component.spirit:description: Advanced eXtensible Interface General Purpose Input/Output (AXI GPIO) core provides a general purpose input/output interface to the AXI interface.
